divs: Sighting DetailsThis UFO, with one small companion orb in one frame, swung over my home in a split second, and was captured in seven frames on my near IR converted webcam. Moved extremely fast, and where it headed was unknown. I get the impression a lot of these UFOs are interested in Calgary's traffic patterns, as I live beside a major intersection in Calgary. Some of these UFOs are hard to see, as they are reflecting so my IR signature.
